data.description: This beautiful 4 bed, 2.5 bath home is chock full of updates - just unpack your belongings and enjoy! Brand new roof + gutters, new driveway, sidewalk + porch, updated flooring throughout, new granite countertops in kitchen, new furnace, front door and more! Formal living and dining rooms. Family room with woodburning fireplace! Spacious eat-in kitchen with generous walk-in pantry, walkout to back deck. First floor powder room and convenient laundry! Owner's suite with cathedral ceiling ft two large closets and attached bath with shower + soaking tub. Expansive ~.46 acre lot with mature trees and space for outdoor activities. All appliances stay! Don't miss this one!
